OL,3,CFraud: Ripping Off The Elderly
OL,5,FMore than half a billion pounds was
OL,6,Fstolen from people aged 65 and over in
OL,7,FEngland and Wales last year - but many
OL,8,Fvictims fear coming forward as those
OL,9,Fstealing from them are family members,
OL,10,Fclose friends or those in positions of
OL,11,Ftrust.
OL,13,FAs the government prepares to
OL,14,Fmodernise power of attorney
OL,15,Fprocedures, Tonight asks is enough
OL,16,Fbeing done to protect older people
OL,17,Ffrom financial abuse?
