OL,5,FAccording to the Office for National
OL,6,FStatistics, approximately 1.5 million
OL,7,Folder adults in England experienced
OL,8,Fsome form of financial abuse in 2020.
OL,9,FBut as victims often don't report the
OL,10,Fabuse when perpetrators are family
OL,11,Fmembers or those in positions of
OL,12,Ftrust, the real figures may be much
OL,13,Fhigher.
