OL,5,FIn Suffolk, safer ageing charity
OL,6,FHourglass is trying to improve
OL,7,Fpeople's awareness of the signs of
OL,8,Ffinancial and economic abuse -
OL,9,Fanything from carers or family members
OL,10,Fusing a person's bank card without
OL,11,Ftheir consent, to pressuring an older
OL,12,Fperson into changing their will, to
OL,13,Fdepriving them of necessities like
OL,14,Ffood and shelter.
