OL,5,FWith an ageing population, and 1 in 2
OL,6,Fof us at risk of being directly
OL,7,Fimpacted by dementia as we get older,
OL,8,Fthe government is encouraging us to
OL,9,Fset up a lasting power of attorney. So
OL,10,Fthat if you do lose capacity, someone
OL,11,Fyou trust is able to act on your
OL,12,Fbehalf to manage your finances and
OL,13,Fcare.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/8
