OL,5,FThe Office of the Public Guardian
OL,6,Fregistered over 1 million lasting
OL,7,Fpowers of attorney in the year 2022-
OL,8,F2023, up 9% on the previous year. The
OL,9,Fgovernment will be updating the
OL,10,Fapplication process for Power of
OL,11,FAttorney using a new act of
OL,12,Fparliament, including bringing in an
OL,13,Fonline-only version of Lasting Power
OL,14,Fof Attorney.
OL,16,FWhether applying online yourself, or
OL,17,Fseeking professional assistance, the
OL,18,Fkey thing is to use power of attorney
OL,19,Fto ensure that your decisions are
OL,20,Fcarried out for you by those you trust.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/8
