OL,5,FFinancial abuse can be difficult to
OL,6,Fspot, but if you have concerns, you
OL,7,Fcan make a report to your local
OL,8,Fauthority's safeguarding team, the
OL,9,Fpolice or the Office of the Public
OL,10,FGuardian.
OL,12,FSome have called for improved
OL,13,Fprocedures by banks when power of
OL,14,Fattorney is being used, with Holly
OL,15,FChantler, Director of Lifetime Lawyers
OL,16,Fsaying:
