OL,5,FThe Office of the Public Guardian is
OL,6,Fworking with financial institutions to
OL,7,Fsupport the use of power of attorney -
OL,8,Fin 2020, the OPG launched a digital
OL,9,Faccess code that can be shared with
OL,10,Fbanks and other organisations to
OL,11,Fconfirm that an LPA is in place.
OL,13,FBritish banks say they are working
OL,14,Fhard to support customers who are
OL,15,Fusing power of attorney, with most
OL,16,Fhigh street banks offering guidance
OL,17,Fand support for both donors and
OL,18,Fattorneys.
